description:
Today we meet swimming trainer Hayami Ayuko from anime "Golden boy".

You asked me to do this LoRA many times here and on pixiv :3

NSFW / SFW Model

LoRA was trained on Animefull-pruned.cpkt due to best compitability with all anime checkpoint models.

0.8 - 1 strength of Lora is the best radius. 

Clip skip 2.

Some necessary tokens for better experience:

Main appearance:

HayamiAyuko, mature female, dark skinned female, dark skin,
black hair, short hair, makeup, brown eyes

recommended:

detailed hair, detailed face, perfect eyes, perfect face

For T-shirt:
White shirt, t-shirt, swimsuit under clothes, barefoot,

optional: white shirt with palm tree print

For swimsuit:

swimsuit, one-piece swimsuit

Also LoRA trained with some NSFW poses. So you can try it with LoRAs or without it.

Advices for better experience:

·         use highres.fix (If you are sure that your prompt is easy for SD); I prefer x4_Fatal_anime_500000_G, animesharp, foolhardy_remacri, siax with 1.5x - 2x upscale.

· use extention after detailer for better faces. It is better than inpaint.

·         use SD Upscale / Ultimate SD Upscale script in img2img;

·         Use inpaint and sketch (or Photopea) for other details;

·         Use Photoshop / Photopea extension.

I will be glad to receive feedback from you and a demonstration of your art with my LoRA!
